            "title": "〈熱門股〉寶齡富錦腎病新藥獲中國藥證 股價寫近10個月新高",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"寶齡富錦\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:寶齡富錦;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/寶齡富錦\">寶齡富錦</a> (1760-TW) 旗下腎病新藥拿百磷 500 毫克膠囊 (Nephoxil 500mg Capsule) 日前取得中國國家藥品監督管理局 (NMPA) 核准藥品註冊，中國藥證到手，激勵寶齡富錦本周股價走揚，周三 (29 日) 衝上 76.4 元，寫近 10 個月以來新高。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">寶齡富錦本周漲幅 7.74%，本周股價最高衝上 76.4 元，一舉站上所有均線，雖然周四 (30 日) 股價走弱，終場收 68.2 元，小跌 0.29%，但仍維持所有均線之上，周線收紅。觀察三大法人籌碼動向，本周合計賣超 181 張。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-3308b125-3726-3e95-863b-a1d95efeb57a-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">寶齡富錦指出，中國的透析患者人口為全球最多，根據中國腎臟病數據登記系統 (CNRDS) 及相關公開資料，截至 2024 年 12 月底，中國透析患者人數約 118.3 萬人。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">寶齡富錦旗下拿百磷字 2014 年起陸續取得多國藥證及上市許可，包括美國、日本、台灣、韓國、泰國以及歐洲。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"寶齡富錦日 K 線圖\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"500\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/sM_YsyNqnulNaAVkBzHnRg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTgyOA--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/cnyes_hk_559/98a0642fe2a1d660fa5d926cf7eb85ec\" width=\"580\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:580px\">寶齡富錦日 K 線圖</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"> </p><p class=\"mb-module-gap read-more-vendor break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span>更多鉅亨報導</span><br/>•<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"〈焦點股〉寶齡富錦腎病新藥中國藥證到手 亮燈漲停\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:〈焦點股〉寶齡富錦腎病新藥中國藥證到手 亮燈漲停;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6434264?utm_source=yahoo&amp;utm_medium=RSS&amp;utm_campaign=relate\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">〈焦點股〉寶齡富錦腎病新藥中國藥證到手 亮燈漲停</a></p></div>",
