        {
            "title": "華爾街期貨在創紀錄高位後小幅上漲;蘋果財報、伊朗衝突成焦點",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Kzz86QXh38NK1PSjPB6Nqw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEF1P0WJ_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 美國股指期貨在週四晚間小幅上漲,此前基準標普500指數和<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"納斯達克綜合指數\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:納斯達克綜合指數;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/納斯達克綜合指數\">納斯達克綜合指數</a>創下歷史新高,投資者在樂觀的企業財報與伊朗衝突帶來的持續地緣政治風險之間尋求平衡。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至美國東部時間20:27(格林威治標準時間00:27),標普500指數期貨上漲0.2%至7,258.0點,納斯達克100指數期貨上漲0.1%至27,626.75點。道指期貨上漲0.2%至49,917.0點。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>標普500指數、納斯達克在財報提振下創歷史新高</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">週四股市收高,標普500指數上漲1%,創紀錄收於7,200點上方,納斯達克綜合指數上漲約0.9%,同樣創下歷史新高。道瓊工業平均指數表現更佳,上漲1.6%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-b224c476-d609-3293-8ced-dfc480566389-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這波漲勢源於主要企業的亮眼業績強化了市場對企業盈利能力的樂觀情緒,幫助市場擺脫了對通脹和地緣政治風險的擔憂。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在盤後交易中,蘋果(NASDAQ:AAPL)股價在發布季度財報後上漲4%,投資者對iPhone需求的韌性以及高利潤率服務業務的持續強勁表現表示歡迎。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">蘋果公布了公司總營收和每股收益的紀錄,iPhone銷售額連續第二個季度增長超過20%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">與此同時,Reddit(NYSE:RDDT)股價在收盤後飆升近13%,受第一季度業績超預期推動,日活躍用戶數超出預期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">投資者也在關注下一批財報,包括雪佛龍公司(NYSE:CVX)、埃克森美孚(NYSE:XOM)和AutoNation Inc(NYSE:AN)將在週五開盤前公布業績。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>伊朗警告若美國發動攻擊將進行「長期而痛苦的打擊」</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">然而,隨著地緣政治風險持續存在,市場情緒仍然脆弱。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">週三Axios報導稱,美國總統唐納德·川普將聽取針對伊朗的新軍事選項簡報,引發了對衝突進一步升級的擔憂。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">伊朗警告稱,任何新的美國攻擊都將引發對該地區美國陣地的「長期而痛苦的打擊」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">霍爾木茲海峽實際上仍處於關閉狀態,擾亂了全球石油運輸的重要航道,並加劇了供應緊張預期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">週四早些時候,布蘭特原油飆升至每桶126美元以上——創四年來最高水平——隨後在獲利了結和貨幣波動的影響下大幅回落至114美元左右。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%8F%AF%E7%88%BE%E8%A1%97%E6%9C%9F%E8%B2%A8%E5%9C%A8%E5%89%B5%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84%E9%AB%98%E4%BD%8D%E5%BE%8C%E5%B0%8F%E5%B9%85%E4%B8%8A%E6%BC%B2-%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E8%B2%A1%E5%A0%B1-%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81%E6%88%90%E7%84%A6%E9%BB%9E-014823808.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-05-01 10:06:26",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "澳新銀行上半年利潤增長6%,削減成本措施帶來更多回報",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/GQcDb8ntU.u8og0ujZxDlw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEAB20CL_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 澳新銀行集團(ASX:ANZ)週五公佈上半年現金利潤表現強勁,在重大重組計劃下持續削減成本的措施提振了這家澳洲銀行的盈利表現。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至3月31日的六個月內,現金利潤年增6%至37.8億澳元(27.2億美元)。該數字較前六個月飆升70%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">營業收入亦小幅改善至112億澳元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">但營業支出年減約2億澳元,這得益於行政總裁<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"馬托斯\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:馬托斯;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/馬托斯\">馬托斯</a>(Nuno Matos)推動的重大重組計劃持續產生回報。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-9330558b-d1eb-3178-bbf8-c8103db704cf-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">馬托斯表示,該銀行正繼續推進重組工作,包括改革高層管理團隊、實施更多削減成本措施,以及完成對Suncorp Bank的整合。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他指出,迄今為止中東戰爭對澳新銀行營運的影響\"微乎其微\"。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">但馬托斯警告稱,這場危機的大部分潛在影響尚未到來,若石油供應長期中斷,將大大增加\"危機從主要的通脹挑戰轉變為更嚴重的供應和增長挑戰\"的可能性。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">澳新銀行作為澳洲最大的銀行之一,宣佈派發每股83澳仙的中期股息。截至3月31日,該銀行的CET1比率為12.39%,較六個月前上升36點子。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%BE%B3%E6%96%B0%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%8A%E5%B9%B4%E5%88%A9%E6%BD%A4%E5%A2%9E%E9%95%B76-%E5%89%8A%E6%B8%9B%E6%88%90%E6%9C%AC%E6%8E%AA%E6%96%BD%E5%B8%B6%E4%BE%86%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%9A%E5%9B%9E%E5%A0%B1-011354558.html",
